              d="M4 4C4 3.44772 4.44772 3 5 3H14H14.5858C14.851 3 15.1054 3.10536 15.2929 3.29289L19.7071 7.70711C19.8946 7.89464 20 8.149 20 8.41421V20C20 20.5523 19.5523 21 19 21H5C4.44772 21 4 20.5523 4 20V4Z"
